title: Steve Rogers and His Daily Routine
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2HkIHIN

by superfamily

Soulmate AU- Steve Rogers often found himself falling into the same daily routine, and the same worry of not finding his soulmate in time. In this universe if you didn’t find your soulmate by age 26 you died; and Steve had accepted that. Until one day his daily routine fell out of place and he happened to meet someone on that not so normal day.

summary:
STANNER - 11/?? 
That first look... that first smile... that first "thank you"... 
You never know what you have until you lose...
caption:
STANNER - 11/??

That first look… that first smile… that first “thank you”… You never know what you have until you lose it… But, oh boy, when you get it back… how much you love it when you get it back. You hug him tightly, just thinking that you don’t want to ever lose him again. Not for a second. Never again.
